  "description": "A nighttime cityscape featuring a brightly lit city skyline and a long bridge extending into the dark water. Above the city, vibrant fireworks explode in a display of red, white, and blue. The city lights create a dense pattern of illumination, with taller buildings standing out against the dark background. The bridge is illuminated with white lights and appears to stretch across a wide body of water. The overall scene is a picturesque view of an urban landscape with a celebratory atmosphere.",
